Text: Unit Outage Revision Cc I started this outage on schedule but was called to work at the Treater Plant on a higher priority Please see the attached revision Thanks Randy Peschka

RE Bushton Unit Outage Cc Jerry Attached is a revision to push the outage back one week In fact it would fit my schedule better this way Thanks Randy Peschka From Jerry nronXgate on PM To Team BushtonMaintenanceET NRON Team BushtonOperationsET NRON Darrell nronXgate Gary nronXgate Steven nronXgate cc Mike PeschkaET NRON Subject RE Bushton Unit Outage Randy the time table you have for this outage is to to replace a section of the exhaust header If we have cold temps the first part of the week can this outage be pushed back a few days Jerry Original Message From BushtonMaintenance Team Sent Thursday February PM To BushtonOperations Team Graves Jerry Schoolcraft Darrell Spraggins Gary Cc BushtonMaintenance Team Peschka Mike Subject Bushton Unit Outage Attachment Thanks Randy Peschka File exhaustheaderdoc
